title: Elk River wins 62-0 in section football playoffs
text: Elk River rolls to 62-0 section playoff victory 10/13/2015, 5:30pm CDT By Jim Paulsen, Star Tribune The Elks raced to 21 points in the first quarter, and the rout was on. Final metro football top 10 10/11/2015, 8:07pm CDT , By Star Tribune This being the final Metro Top 10 of the season — rankings become irrelevant once playoffs begin — it’s a good time to reflect to see how the preseason rankings stack up against what actually occurred. New methodology used in football playoff seeding 10/11/2015, 9:00pm CDT , By JIM PAULSEN, Star Tribune Saturday was perhaps the most controversial day of the high school football season — section seeding day, when teams find out where they rank in their section and who their first-round opponent will be.
